(4403, 209, 'rows_3_col1', '<h4 class="p1">WHY SEQUENTRA?</h4>\r\n<p class="p1">The property data management module, lease administration, is the cornerstone of our application. Global organisations have managed their real estate portfolios using Sequentra since 1999. Our system has always been web based and has proven itself for a vast range of corporate needs. This module is used to manage over 1 billion square feet of properties in over 150 countries.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Our account managers at Sequentra are real estate professionals who you can rely upon to make certain our tools meet the requirements of your organisation today and into the future.</p>'),
