(6965, 258, 'rows_7_col2_a', '<h4>WE HAVE HIGH STANDARDS.</h4>\r\nWith the new lease accounting changes impacting both current and future leasing strategy globally, companies need to have a plan in place.\r\n\r\nDesigned to control, manage and unlock data within an organisation, Sequentra provides clients with the best decision making facts to build a competitive advantage. It was created with the purpose of preparing clients for audit in a fully compatible manner for both IFRS 16 and FASB (ASC 842), as well as having a central, organised location for all of their data - data is key when it comes to compliance.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a class="green-btn" href="#">REQUEST A DEMO</a>'),
